# Deploy and verify after push

After pushing to `main`, deploy and verify production:
```bash
vercel --token $VERCEL_TOKEN --prod --scope $VERCEL_SCOPE --yes
```
Task is not done until production shows the change.

## Vercel Hobby limits
- Cron: max one run per day per job (no `*/15 * * * *`)
- If deploy fails due to cron frequency, reduce to daily